automatically generating the license header is not realistic, if you want to automatically generate license header, you don't even need a plugin, the IDEA has such ability to include a license when creating a new class (will attach a screenshot later 
 if you need ), the reason why it's not acceptable to generate license header in maven lifecycle is as follows:
We check the license header in maven lifecycle, and report errors if it doesn't adhere to Apache's policy, but if you generate the license header in maven lifecycle too, it hides the errors and the generated license header won't be included in the source codes, which is dangerous for an Apache project.
